    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_154949900" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/154949900" />
    <a title="Bechai Jalea" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/3076633-bechai-jalea"><img alt="Bechai Jalea" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1356744590p2/3076633.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/154949900?book_show_action=true">Mar 17, 2011</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Bechai Jalea" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Bechai Jalea" href="/user/show/3076633-bechai-jalea">Bechai Jalea</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer154949900" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16977262795272342457"><br/>Depression caught up with me while reading this book. I was already touched by its condensed version (Chinese Cinderella) and reading this book felt like rubbing in the &quot;touchy feeling&quot; even more. <br/><br/>My heart goes to Aunt Baba who survived being a spinster, a worker in a male-dominated labor force, and a victim of war. It&apos;s amazing how a person endures, and live through life amid utmost cruelty. <br/><br/></span>
  <span id="freeText16977262795272342457" style="display:none"><br />Depression caught up with me while reading this book. I was already touched by its condensed version (Chinese Cinderella) and reading this book felt like rubbing in the "touchy feeling" even more. <br /><br />My heart goes to Aunt Baba who survived being a spinster, a worker in a male-dominated labor force, and a victim of war. It's amazing how a person endures, and live through life amid utmost cruelty. <br /><br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="16977262795272342457" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


